{"type": "article", "id": 33327, "title": "木制灯，不知为何有一种童话的感觉｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2016-10-15T00:12:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 31410, "name": "Almleuchten"}, {"id": 33954, "name": "灯具设计"}, {"id": 33955, "name": "SHIINA+NARDI DESIGN"}, {"id": 33956, "name": "Manifattura Italian Design"}, {"id": 33957, "name": "Hurlu"}, {"id": 33958, "name": "Slow Wood"}, {"id": 23190, "name": "haim evgi"}, {"id": 33959, "name": "Michael Warren"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 367, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161015003143Md9mUq6QSb2xlOaN.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><p class=\"\">作为一种常见材料，你可能已经在不少家居产品中感受到了木料特有的温润质感。对于设计师而言，木头易于雕刻的特性则意味着它们能更好地实现一些特别的创意。本周的主题就是这些烘托出木料天然魅力的灯饰。</p><p>          </p><h3>Teca by Slow Wood</h3><p>          </p><p><a href=\"http://slowwood.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Slow Wood</a> 是一间以生产木雕为主的意大利初创公司，这盏造型优雅的 Teca 灯是它联手设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.shiinanardidesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SHINNA+NARDI DESIGN</a> 共同打造而成的。每一个灯罩都是由工匠 Lorenzo Franceschinis 选用樱桃木亲手雕刻而成的，因为它的纤薄你能在亮灯后清楚地看到边缘的颜色变化。为了让整体效果更加完整，SHINNA+NARDI DESIGN 还邀请到灯光公司 <a href=\"http://www.feenbo.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Feenbo</a> 的工匠制作了与木雕艺术相当合拍的玻璃罩，使得整个灯饰更具有连贯性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014164430dapjfeSvULZrQuk9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014164432P3M6CBKZcas7m9Lo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101416442934YTjRKVWhyOr6BI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014164431qEzwt35ZerJfaUs2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.651589\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014164433voT3hNdJigtsfMek.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014164447ombBr4wIAJg3PS6c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Stacked lamp by Michael Warren</h3><p>专注于 DIY 的美国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.michaelsaurus.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mike Warren</a> 此前相中了由意大利工作室 <a href=\"http://www.designmid.com/index.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Manifattura Italian Design</a> 推出的 <a href=\"http://www.designmid.com/eng/babele.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">Babele</a> 木灯，令人望而却步的 660 欧元定价让他决定以此为原型设计一款能让人们自己动手打造的木块灯。如果你打算自己动手试一试的话，你可以通过<a href=\"http://www.instructables.com/id/stacked-lamp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>了解更详细的操作，还能下载 Warren 准备的模版。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014210053PnhKoQ87mtbwXex4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854688\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014210053ZWc2nM5sRoOhA7x6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014210053qtVpdP8a5QKsvoNG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014210054EMkOjH5mgRu4vo9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014210054tqumnWfi1NhCR24B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.854688\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014210054mh6oYQENd0D397TP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kavo by Haim Evgi</h3><p>          </p><p>对于不希望从头开始制作灯饰的人来说，来自以色列设计师 <a href=\"http://www.haimevgi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Haim Evgi</a> 的 KAVO DIY 木制台灯是一个更简单的选择。台灯共有六个部件，通过四个螺丝就能将很快地组装起来，扁平化的包装也为运输提供了便利。虽然摒弃了传统的灯罩设计，两块模版交错形成的立体感却相当独特。这是它的<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/kavo-diy-table-lamp-haim-evgi-01-25-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 149 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014163310tvHphIP6s27QoVw1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014163309Xp7uwNcT60FaZbzO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610141633062VRb9FvkrnNT6YXK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014163309kdhZGLpKxBO9XJg6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014163309tsHdM4bjwI9va5CD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.351000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BEC portable lamp by Hurlu</h3><p>          </p><p>当法国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.hurludesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hurlu</a> 的设计师们注意到吉伦特（Gironde）的一间箱子工厂每天都会产生大量的废弃木料时，他们决定设计一些简单又实用的产品减少对木材的浪费，由此诞生了木制品系列 BEC。为了提醒人们木料的历史，灯具被打造成了盒状，两面则用上色的栅栏封住。灯具分为壁灯和台灯两款，壁灯打开后配合墙上的光影，远远看去就好像一个领结，简洁有趣。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/HURLU\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些灯具，售价从 79.15 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014165003JsPxGqD2WOA5M48a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014165004GfYK8sxlZyaAvVJ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014165004y01jWpM9hQINloHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014165004nPM2QdSi57p6CZul.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707018\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014165004kKT2zr4YhSHiexVJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Almleuchten by Felix Sehr &amp; Harald Hofer</h3><p class=\"\">奥地利独立灯具品牌 Almleuchten 由 Felix Fehr 和 Harald Hofer 共同创立，从木料的裂痕和纹路中透露出的沧桑感赋予了灯具一种天然的魅力。Almleuchten 所使用的大部分木料均取自蒂罗尔（Tyrol）当地高山上废弃的木屋，因此每一盏灯都是独一无二的。得益于特殊的切割工艺，灯具在点亮后还会散发出温暖的红光。如果你对它们感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.almleuchten.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>进行订购。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155402qJ5GBQyrCEdR2vSI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155402KLo2wBtcsgvPROim.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155402vqrTGs9cKu8yxmId.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155402J2mxSRfvULiIQ6oC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155402qXnv1sSJHdxbwuLE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610141554023H9YZ2BFMVLOR7wJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.698333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wooden lamps by Sara Collet Watson</h3><p class=\"\">来自美国加州的 <a href=\"http://www.driftwith.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sara Collet Watson</a> 热衷于制作各种造型独特的灯具或是灯光装置。这些漂亮的木制台灯都由她亲手打造而成，木料表面或疏或密地穿凿了许多大小不一的圆孔，在灯光的映衬下带来一种通透的感觉。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/LightingBySara\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些灯具，售价从 44 到 145 美元不等。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155139N1xdu7K0ojt6R9ar.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155140h8aQFAqOyRkHr0gz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155140glKRCA0IyFdJmpk6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155140NmIAjkvnOHfy8QUM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155139ehpW8KN9sH2XrZfY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161014155140Td8gjekDphZJ2i7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}